Description:
~~~~~~~~~~~~

About This Game Life on Earth is unsustainable. Humanity must seek a new home
but the only planet found is very hostile. You were sent on a expedition to
slay the monsters inhabiting the surface of this planet. In this adventure
you end up being the villain.Game contains two basic controls, many puzzles
and lots of guns and enemies. (12 guns and more than 20 monsters)

~~~~~~~
Unrar, mount/burn, install the game, copy crack and play!
